videos.headline: McKinney returns INT 80 yards for Alabama pick-6
videos.description: Alabama's Xavier McKinney hauls in the interception and goes 80 yards to the house for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McKinney returns INT 80 yards for Alabama pick-6) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Tua: Being here uplifts my spirits
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa thanks everyone from the Alabama fans to his parents as he recovers from hip surgery, and says supporting his team from the sidelines has been uplifting.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Tua: Being here uplifts my spirits) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Western Carolina QB catches his own pass and fumbles
videos.description: Tyrie Adams catches his own pass after it's tipped, then tries to run but is stripped giving the ball back to Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Western Carolina QB catches his own pass and fumbles) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Robinson Jr. goes through the defense for the Bama TD
videos.description: Alabama running back Brian Robinson Jr. runs through the defense and into the end zone for the 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson Jr. goes through the defense for the Bama TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Alabama's Harris powers his way into the end zone
videos.description: Alabama running back Najee Harris hauls in the pass, then shows off his strength en route to a 12-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alabama's Harris powers his way into the end zone) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Tua's brother throws a TD
videos.description: Taulia Tagovailoa, the younger brother of Tua, connects with DeVonta Smith for a 15-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Robinson weaves through the defense for the TD
videos.description: Alabama running back Keilan Robinson weaves through the defense and ends up in the end zone for the 46-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson weaves through the defense for the TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Jones tosses 3 TD passes as Alabama cruises to win
videos.description: Mac Jones throws three touchdown passes and Tua Tagovailoa's younger brother, Taulia, adds another in Alabama's 66-3 win over Western Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Jones tosses 3 TD passes as Alabama cruises to win) 2019/11/23 SOTFULL
